Hi Niles,

Thank you for giving us the opportunity to consider you for the position of Software Engineer, Server - Diablo IV. We regret to inform you that we will not be moving forward with your candidacy at this time. We will retain your information in our system and may reach out to you if future roles match your skillset.

Regards, BLIZZARD ENTERTAINMENT, INC. Recruiting

Hi Niles, 

 While the interviewing team was impressed with your skills and enjoyed getting to know you, after a careful review, we’ve unfortunately determined that we do not have a position that is a strong match for your qualifications at this time. Due to company policy, we are unable to provide specific interview feedback, but I’d be more than happy to set aside some time to discuss anything outside of that.

Anni Demberger Palantir Technologies | Recruiting

Hi Niles, 

 Thank you for your application for the Associate Engine Programmer position at Rockstar San Diego. We have reviewed your application materials, however we have determined that they are not quite a match for the role at this point in time.We appreciate your time and interest in Rockstar Games and wish you all the best in your job search. 

The Rockstar Games Talent Acquisition Team
